    <introduction>
      <para>
        According to the use case, you may choose one of the following installation methods. There are also two channels available: Stable release, and Nightly release.
      </para>
      <para>
        Stable version will be released every month, it contains all new features completely developped, tested and available for different language.
      </para>
      <para>
        Nightly version is released several times per week. It contains the latest features and bug fixes in preview mode. means these features may complete and available only in English.
      </para>
      <para>
        Whatever the version used, Hummingbird introduced a news feed in the software. You will be notified when a new version is available.
      </para>
      <autoOutline />
    </introduction>

