    <section address="Section1">
      <title>Prerequisites</title>
      <content>
        <para>
          The Hummingbird project is built upon .NET Framework 4.6.1.
          You must have .NET Framework 4.6.1 or later version installed before running the
          software.
        </para>

        <para>
          The following operation systems have already .NET Framework 4.6.1 pre-installed. 
        </para>
        <list class="bullet">
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows 10</para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows Server 2016</para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>Or the newer version of Windows and Windows Server</para>
          </listItem>          
        </list>

        <para>
          When using following version of Windows, please make sure the .NET Framework 4.6.1 is installed. 
          <externalLink>
            <linkText>from this link.</linkText>
            <linkUri>https://www.microsoft.com/en-US/download/details.aspx?id=30653</linkUri>
          </externalLink>
        </para>
        <list class="bullet">
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows Vista SP2</para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows 7 SP1</para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows 8</para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows 8.1</para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows Server 2008 SP2</para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows Server 2008 R2 SP1</para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows Server 2012</para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>Windows Server R2</para>
          </listItem>
        </list>
      </content>
    </section>

    <section address="_Toc515307882">
      <!--h1-->
      <title>Installation instructions</title>
      <content>
        <para>
          There are several ways to install Hummingbird according to your use case.
        </para>

        <para>
          When using Hummingbird on a Desktop machine for Test and Automation by using the GUI application, the simplest way is to apply the ClickOnce version. It ensures that you are always running the latest version of software. To install with ClickOnce, Please refer to ClickOnce Installation. Please note that ClickOnce installer contains only Hummingbird app. Command Line Interface and Report Viewer is not included.
        </para>

        <para>
          If you planned to run Hummingbird on a Server Machine, or the machines used for DevOps pipeline. You should use the Windows Installer or Zip version to ensure all components – especially Hummingbird CLI – are included.
        </para>

        <para>
          To install Hummingbird, please choose the following installation guide
        </para>
        <alert class="caution">
          <para>Download and install any version of Hummingbird, means you accept the License Agreement</para>
        </alert>
        <list class="bullet">
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <link xlink:href="a95ea83d-733b-4a07-b290-438514fbcbb5" />
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <link xlink:href="f7a36b1b-4cf2-4130-99c9-460787e5b2fe"/>
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              <link xlink:href="cb60599c-39e3-48df-b079-03533657ba3a" />
            </para>
          </listItem>
        </list>

        <alert class="note">
          <para>
            You can install multiple versions of Hummingbird from different media, But All hummingbird instances share the same copy of Profile, History and Settings.
          </para>
        </alert>
      </content>
    </section>

    <section address="enterprise">
      <title>Enterprise users</title>
      <content>
        <para>If you are using Hummingbird in your Enterprise PC, Downloading Executable files (Installer) may be blocked by Group Polocies set by your security departement. Please make sure you are authroized to use the software. In other hand, Except Service Simulation, All other features of Hummingbird do not require Administration previlege, you can use the ZIP version and follow the instructions</para>
      </content>
    </section>
    
